        "de158e68-5d0d-4819-a625-e2dabdff87d1": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Who is Dr. Elias Velin and why should I trust him?",
            "heading_size": "medium",
            "icon": "search",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "collapse_icon": "carret",
            "display_top_border": true,
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p>The author is presented as a former AI ethics architect turned whistleblower. Whether you see him as real or a pseudonym, what matters is that the codes are drawn from <strong>leaked reports, suppressed studies, and insider knowledge</strong> that you won’t find in mainstream AI coverage.</p>",
            "page": "",
            "margin_top": 24,
            "margin_bottom": 0
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_RDaXPM": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Is this a story or a factual analysis?",
            "heading_size": "medium",
            "icon": "book_5",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "collapse_icon": "carret",
            "display_top_border": true,
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p>It’s written like a first-person journal, but every cascade ties back to <strong>documented AI incidents, research papers, and ongoing experiments</strong>. Think of it as reality delivered in narrative form, both gripping and disturbingly real.</p>",
            "page": "",
            "margin_top": 24,
            "margin_bottom": 0
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_TdYymG": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "What exactly are “the 12 codes”?",
            "heading_size": "medium",
            "icon": "extension",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "collapse_icon": "carret",
            "display_top_border": true,
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p>They’re not just theories. Each code is a systemic weak point where AI can trigger collapse: from supply chains and finance, to information control and even water systems. Together, they form a hidden blueprint of how civilization can unravel under quiet automation.</p>",
            "page": "",
            "margin_top": 24,
            "margin_bottom": 0
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_RkbTyh": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How soon do I get the book after purchase?",
            "heading_size": "medium",
            "icon": "⏱",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "collapse_icon": "carret",
            "display_top_border": true,
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p>Immediately. Once your payment is processed, you’ll receive a direct download link. No shipping, no waiting, the book is in your inbox right away.</p>",
            "page": "",
            "margin_top": 24,
            "margin_bottom": 0
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_MrY8Ha": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Can this book actually help me prepare?",
            "heading_size": "medium",
            "icon": "shield",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "collapse_icon": "carret",
            "display_top_border": true,
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p>Yes. Beyond raising awareness, the steps highlight <strong>warning signs to watch for, mental frameworks to adopt, and areas where you can build resilience</strong> in your personal and professional life. It’s not just a book about fear, it’s about foresight.</p>",
            "page": "",
            "margin_top": 24,
            "margin_bottom": 0
          }
        }
      },
