        "text_FMCUGY": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<h2></h2><p>When Geoffrey Hinton quit Google, they tried to silence him.</p><p>When OpenAI went dark, they called it \"competitive advantage.\"</p><p>When 36% of AI scientists warned of extinction-level risks, the media buried it on page 12.</p><p><strong>They're terrified you'll discover what's really happening.</strong></p><p>Because once you know the 12 Codes, you can't be controlled. You can't be replaced. You can't be erased.</p><h2>Two Paths Forward</h2><p><strong>Path 1</strong>: Ignore this warning. Keep believing AI is just a helpful tool. Wake up in 2030 jobless, watching your children struggle in a world you don't recognize, wondering why nobody warned you.</p><p><strong>Path 2</strong>: Arm yourself with the truth. Learn the 12 Codes. Prepare your family. Join the resistance before it's too late.</p>",
            "text_style": "body"
          }
        }
