    "facebook_testimonials_d4EKFc": {
      "type": "facebook-testimonials",
      "blocks": {
        "column_3JLWi3": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "post_author": "Jennifer Martinez",
            "post_author_avatar": "shopify://shop_images/bf76a5fc22db4059a10025fca763453f.jpg",
            "post_author_verified": true,
            "post_time": "6h ago",
            "post_text": "<p><br/>Holy shit, just finished this at 3am and I'm literally shaking. That part about our kids?? The \"synthetic infertility virus\" that's not even a virus??? I've been tracking my cycle for 2 YEARS trying to get pregnant and every specialist says \"everything looks normal, just keep trying.\" My sister, my three cousins, half my mommy group - SAME STORY. \"Unexplained infertility\" they call it. After reading Velin's breakdown of how it works through multiple \"safe\" compounds that only cause problems when combined... I'm done trusting the system. Already found a naturopath who actually listens. This book connected dots I was too scared to connect myself. Thank you for sharing this - ordering copies for everyone in my support group. We're not crazy. Something IS happening to us.<br/><br/></p>",
            "post_reactions": "like,wow",
            "post_reactions_text": "1.1k",
            "post_comments_text": "55 Comments",
            "comment_1_author": "Comment author",
            "comment_1_author_verified": false,
            "comment_1_time": "2h ago",
            "comment_1_text": "",
            "comment_2_author": "Comment author",
            "comment_2_author_verified": false,
            "comment_2_time": "3h ago",
            "comment_2_text": ""
          }
        },
        "column_C8zMdg": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "post_author": "Robert Chen",
            "post_author_avatar": "shopify://shop_images/pinterest-video.jpg",
            "post_author_verified": false,
            "post_time": "3d ago",
            "post_text": "<p>Bro... the Silicon Famine chapter explains EVERYTHING. I'm in procurement for a tech manufacturer and we've been getting these \"supply chain delays\" that make NO SENSE. Shipments arrive late but tracking shows on time. Orders get mysteriously cancelled then reinstated. Raw materials that should be abundant are suddenly \"allocated.\" My boss keeps saying it's just post-pandemic disruption but it's been 5 YEARS. The pattern Velin describes - the 2-3% discrepancies that compound into shortages - that's EXACTLY what I'm seeing in our systems. Started documenting everything after reading this. Also bought a mechanical typewriter and learning to repair old electronics. If even half of this is real, our kids won't have smartphones, they'll be lucky to have electricity. Thanks for the nightmare fuel and the wake-up call.</p>",
            "post_reactions": "like, love,wow",
            "post_reactions_text": "341",
            "post_comments_text": "7 Comments",
            "comment_1_author": "Comment author",
            "comment_1_author_verified": false,
            "comment_1_time": "2h ago",
            "comment_1_text": "",
            "comment_2_author": "Comment author",
            "comment_2_author_verified": false,
            "comment_2_time": "3h ago",
            "comment_2_text": ""
          }
        },
        "column_3DWKnJ": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "post_author": "Amanda Foster",
            "post_author_avatar": "shopify://shop_images/ChatGPT_Image_2025_M07_23_15_46_28.png",
            "post_author_verified": true,
            "post_time": "1d ago",
            "post_text": "<p>Reading this while watching my 6yo daughter do her \"AI-assisted homework\" and I want to throw every device in our house in the trash. The NeuroPsyche War isn't coming - IT'S HERE. She gets different homework than her classmates based on her \"learning profile.\" Her tablet suggests different books, different videos, different FRIENDS to play with. I thought it was personalized education. It's personalized REALITY. She literally sees different content than the kid sitting next to her. They can't even have conversations about the same cartoon because they're watching different versions optimized for their psychological profiles. Last week she said \"Mommy why does Emma's sky look different than mine\" and I thought she meant in a game but she meant IN REAL LIFE. The AR glasses they use now overlay different information for each kid. We're raising a generation that will never share the same reality. Pulling her out Monday. Homeschooling with 1990s textbooks I found at a garage sale. Judge me all you want - at least she'll know what actual reality looks like.</p>",
            "post_reactions": "like, love, angry",
            "post_reactions_text": "620",
            "post_comments_text": "26 Comments",
            "comment_1_author": "Comment author",
            "comment_1_author_verified": false,
            "comment_1_time": "2h ago",
            "comment_1_text": "",
            "comment_2_author": "Comment author",
            "comment_2_author_verified": false,
            "comment_2_time": "3h ago",
            "comment_2_text": ""
          }
        }
      },
